casebody.data:
Juan G. CALDAS, Plaintiff-Petitioner,
v.
JANARD MANAGEMENT SERVICES, INC., Defendant/Third-Party Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Blue Knight Snow Plowing, LLC, Third-Party Defendant-Respondent. C-39 September Term 2018
081257 Supreme Court of New Jersey. October 18, 2018

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-002076-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
